Package com.epam.onlineshop.command.orders

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddProductToListCommand
    The AddProductToListCommand class responsible for add product that the customer has decided to buy and and place it in a temporary collection.
    ChangeOrderCommand
    The ChangeOrderCommand class responsible for update delivery condition.
    CheckoutCommand
    The CheckoutCommand class responsible for checkout order.
    CheckoutProcessCommand
    The CheckoutProcessCommand class responsible for order processing.
    DeleteOrderCommand
    The DeleteOrderCommand class responsible for delete order from database by orderId.
    DeleteTempProductsOrderCommand
    The DeleteTempProductsOrderCommand class responsible for delete from temp collection(list).
    PrintOrdersForUserCommand
    The PrintOrdersForUserCommand class responsible for print all orders located in user-basket.
    SearchUnprocessedOrdersCommand
    The SearchUnprocessedOrdersCommand class responsible for search only unprocessed orders and show it in table.
    ShowOrdersListCommand
    The ShowOrdersListCommand class responsible for print all information of orders.
    ShowTempProductsOrderCommand
    The ShowTempProductsOrderCommand class responsible for print orders to concrete user from temp collection.
    SortOrdersCommand
    The SortOrdersCommand class responsible for sort orders by lead time.
